==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Southcottian
<hw>South*cot"ti*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl.
Hist.)</fld> <def>A follower of Joanna <xex>Southcott</xex> (1750-1814),
an Englishwoman who, professing to have received a miraculous calling,
preached and prophesied, and committed many impious
absurdities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

